xxl.core.relational.resultSets
Class VirtualTable

java.lang.Object
  xxl.core.relational.resultSets.DecoratorResultSet
      xxl.core.relational.resultSets.VirtualTable
All Implemented Interfaces:
ResultSet
public class VirtualTable
extends DecoratorResultSet

This class is a wrapper for result sets with the intention to receive an instance of the VTI (Virtual Table Interface) in order to use the wrapped result set in a FROM clause of an SQL-J statement.

IMPORTANT: the function SET_RESULTSET has to be defined before any call to a constructor, i.e. before using NEW VirtualTable() in a FROM-clause.
